f2ccea6fbe554757b5ddf95061c52cfed11a725544db5597c43dd4681297ec273c0e24a558a80c9f36b9db7fd18df9730c21b9b707c921771199e079d27b07de  0001-Fall-back-to-gettext-module-on-systems-that-don-t-us.patch"
